# ---- Pre-Show Programming ----
Store Cue 1 "House Open"
Store Cue 2 "Pre-Set"
Store Cue 3 "Downstage Wash"

# ---- Fixture Selection ----
Select Fixture 1 Thru 10
Fixture 11 At 75
Channel 1 Thru 4 At Full

# ---- Variables ----
SetVar $sceneIndex = 1
Goto Cue $sceneIndex

# ---- Executor Assignment ----
Assign Sequence 1 At Executor 1
Copy Sequence 1 At Sequence 2
Label Sequence 2 "Backup"
Go
